{"tid":2250153,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"巴基斯坦解除對中國抖音海外版TikTok的禁令","createTime":"2020-10-20T02:09:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T02:20:07.000Z","uid":295230,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"392a234065bd6aeeab0af30378edaca5c68e9eec","tid":2250153,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T02:09:20.000Z","msg":"巴基斯坦政府解除對中國抖音海外版TikTok的禁令，有條件恢復TikTok在當地的服務。<br />\n<br />\n巴基斯坦電信管理局說，TikTok承諾依據社會規範和巴基斯坦法律審核內容，確保上傳非法內容的用戶被屏蔽在平台外，由此解除對TikTok的禁令，但TikTok必須嚴格遵守相關條件，確保平台不得用於傳播粗俗或不雅內容，不得濫用社會價值，否則當局會實施永久禁令。<br />\n<br />\n巴基斯坦今個月9日以未過濾不道德內容為由，禁用TikTok。"},{"pid":"776eb66ebd57d71276d37cb40152f381d1f82897","tid":2250153,"uid":295230,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T02:09:38.000Z","msg":"無D骨氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1642e988cb37eeeaa5db566d1aa75ac7aabbd9a3","tid":2250153,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T02:09:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1bf7d8411b3d8ba243193e635d8b46757477030","tid":2250153,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T02:13:44.000Z","msg":"..有冇搞錯<br />\n<br />\n美國果邊tiktok ban 又冇哂聲氣<br />\n<br />\n全世界都對支那低聲下氣嗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed20060934d085c1da370ea04b2c2ebd03acfe8b","tid":2250153,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T02:15:47.000Z","msg":"因為唔係海外版  巴基斯坦自古以來都係中國領土"},{"pid":"f0eec269d9ff2d7af69aaaf72150daffe410c562","tid":2250153,"uid":366906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T02:20:07.000Z","msg":"始終係支那既好朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}